    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8479_276730_000042_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8479/276730/8479_276730_000042_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8479",
        "content": "\"L.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8479_276730_000043_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8479/276730/8479_276730_000043_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8479",
        "content": "\"The reasons are special for twelve o'clock.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8479_276730_000044_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8479/276730/8479_276730_000044_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8479",
        "content": "(Signed) \"G.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8479_276730_000047_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8479/276730/8479_276730_000047_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8479",
        "content": "\"Sir: The Government of the Confederate States has hitherto forborne from any hostile demonstration against Fort Sumter, in the hope that the Government of the United States, with a view to the amicable adjustment of all questions between the two Governments, and to avert the calamities of war, would voluntarily evacuate it.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8479_276730_000048_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8479/276730/8479_276730_000048_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8479",
        "content": "\"But the Confederate States can no longer delay assuming actual possession of a fortification commanding the entrance of one of their harbors, and necessary to its defense and security.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8479_276730_000049_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8479/276730/8479_276730_000049_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8479",
        "content": "\"I am ordered by the Government of the Confederate States to demand the evacuation of Fort Sumter.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8479_276730_000049_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8479/276730/8479_276730_000049_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8479",
        "content": "My aides, Colonel Chesnut and Captain Lee, are authorized to make such demand of you.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8479_276730_000049_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8479/276730/8479_276730_000049_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8479",
        "content": "All proper facilities will be afforded for the removal of yourself and command, together with company arms and property, and all private property, to any post in the United States which you may elect.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8479_276730_000049_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8479/276730/8479_276730_000049_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8479",
        "content": "The flag which you have upheld so long and with so much fortitude, under the most trying circumstances, may be saluted by you on taking it down.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8479_276730_000050_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8479/276730/8479_276730_000050_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8479",
        "content": "\"Colonel Chesnut and Captain Lee will, for a reasonable time, await your answer.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8479_276730_000051_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8479/276730/8479_276730_000051_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8479",
        "content": "\"I am, sir, very respectfully, your obedient servant,",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8479_276730_000052_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8479/276730/8479_276730_000052_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8479",
        "content": "(Signed) \"G.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8479_276730_000058_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8479/276730/8479_276730_000058_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8479",
        "content": "\"Thanking you for the fair, manly, and courteous terms proposed, and for the high compliment paid me,",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8479_276730_000066_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8479/276730/8479_276730_000066_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8479",
        "content": "You are thus to avoid the effusion of blood.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8479_276730_000066_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8479/276730/8479_276730_000066_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8479",
        "content": "If this or its equivalent be refused, reduce the fort as your judgment decides to be most practicable.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8479_276730_000067_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8479/276730/8479_276730_000067_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8479",
        "content": "(Signed) \"L.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8479_276730_000071_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8479/276730/8479_276730_000071_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8479",
        "content": "\"If you will state the time at which you will evacuate Fort Sumter, and agree that in the mean time you will not use your guns against us, unless ours shall be employed against Fort Sumter, we will abstain from opening fire upon you.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8479_276730_000071_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8479/276730/8479_276730_000071_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8479",
        "content": "You are therefore requested to communicate to them an open answer.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8479_276730_000097_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8479/276730/8479_276730_000097_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8479",
        "content": "Inasmuch as it was known to the Confederate commander that the \"controlling instructions\" were already issued, and that the \"additional supplies\" were momentarily expected; inasmuch, also, as any attempt to introduce the supplies would compel the opening of fire upon the vessels bearing them under the flag of the United States-thereby releasing Major Anderson from his pledge-it is evident that his conditions could not be accepted.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    }
]